nctioning as an additional airfoil rather than as a prey-capture device. Limb proportions and retention of claws on all digits indicate that the new bat may have been an agile climber that employed quadrupedal locomotion and under-branch hanging behaviour.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Simmons, Nancy B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Seymour, Kevin L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Habersetzer, J\u00f6rg", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gunnell, Gregg F.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/72752c13d5a079db3f12928293d681b1", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/ea323972d94a0b81fb1d132da94445956718e00c17052a053593af37eca9e00b", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/JSB7H6ZQ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/JSB7H6ZQ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/61c3b93cfcf3d4e166cabb52c30af2c8!/b160235-163360", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "7180", "pages": "818-821", "title": "Nature", "volume": "451"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/72752c13d5a079db3f12928293d681b1"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:JSB7H6ZQ"}, {"identifier": "10.1038/nature06549"}], "communities": [{"id": 